data.description: LOCATION!!!!  This well-maintained 1728 sq ft Colonial-style home has 4 bedrooms, 2 FULL BATHS Completely updated. Spacious and bright new kitchen with Quartz countertop Stainless steels appliances, freshly painted thru out the entire house. Gas stove, Spacious living & dining rooms, full bath & good-sized bedroom most with stunning hardwoods. This move-in ready home features another full bath, deep walk-in closet, & 3 additional bedrooms – including a large front-to-back master! roof (2018), driveway (2020), Gas heat & hot water, huge garage, vinyl siding (2004), & 2 sheds – Nothing left to do in this beauty but move in. This home offers a warm & comfortable refuge as well as plenty of space to entertain inside and out on its 1.3-acre lot!! New Pressure treated deck (2023) Nestled in a quiet neighborhood yet close to all amenities and major routes. This home will not last schedule your private showing.
